{
  "id": "RAW_eb79df92",
  "title": "56 倍加速生成式策略：西交大提出 EfficientFlow，迈向高效具身智能",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651007467&idx=3&sn=4ed28ddf99c067488e896b74769bcec0",
  "date": "2025-12-16 04:09:00",
  "author": "机器之心",
  "siteName": "机器之心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">本文共同第一作者为西安交通大学硕士生常建磊和博士生梅若风。柯炜为西安交通大学副教授。论文通讯作者为西安交通大学教授许翔宇，其研究方向涵盖三维视觉、生成式 AI 与具身智能（个人主页：<a href=\"https://xuxy09.github.io/）。\" target=\"_blank\">https://xuxy09.github.io/）。</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">生成式模型正在成为机器人和具身智能领域的重要范式，它能够从高维视觉观测中直接生成复杂、灵活的动作策略，在操作、抓取等任务中表现亮眼。但在真实系统中，这类方法仍面临两大「硬伤」：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">一是训练极度依赖大规模演示数据，二是推理阶段需要大量迭代，动作生成太慢，难以实时控制。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">针对这一核心瓶颈，西安交通大学研究团队提出了全新的生成式策略学习方法&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">EfficientFlow</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。该方法通过将</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">等变建模与高效流匹配（Flow Matching）深度融合</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">在显著提升数据效率的同时，大幅压缩推理所需的迭代步数</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，在多个机器人操作基准上实现了 SOTA 的性能，并将推理速度提升一个数量级以上。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">相关论文《EfficientFlow: Efficient Equivariant Flow Policy Learning for Embodied AI》</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">已被 AAAI 2026 接收，代码已开源</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503523764\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6763317599460553\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1483\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1483\" data-height=\"1003\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"391\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=93f28860&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42evqQIRibKlic33xDpHia3UzYDyJ3ibS0uPnUicLT87TtssSkp62ujXKezLFpR1jIdIquQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">论文地址：<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2512.02020\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/pdf/2512.02020</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">项目主页：<a href=\"https://efficientflow.github.io/\" target=\"_blank\">https://efficientflow.github.io/</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">GitHub：<a href=\"https://github.com/chang-jl/EfficientFlow\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/chang-jl/EfficientFlow</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">技术亮点：用物理直觉重塑生成式策略</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">1. 加速度正则化：让生成轨迹更直、更快</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">传统流匹配的一大痛点是学习到的流场曲率过大，导致推理时仍需多步迭代才能拟合。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">怎么让生成轨迹变直？ EfficientFlow 的设计灵感源于物理直觉：现实中平滑的运动，往往加速度很小。 因此，EfficientFlow 在损失函数中引入了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">加速度正则项</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，鼓励样本从噪声分布向数据分布演化的过程也是平滑且接近匀速的：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503523717\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1600633914421553\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"631\" style=\"width:297px;height:48px;\" type=\"block\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/KmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42evqQIRibKlicmOgQ9uZ1w6hAPNjibqOibdaLU6zzycI6Tu3dEspFCgSLLjLAdkJNcDNQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"631.8343949044586\" data-cropy2=\"102.11464968152866\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0d9f763f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FKmXPKA19gWibpJ08gskIzfop6hz3Fal6PQvsNmK1AhJXHPJfkCeMNeJdbAyUoykuiae2bcMY1Uts9JnR89ic60CSg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">其中</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503523721\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0454545454545454\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"44\" style=\"width:20px;height:21px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8602db3c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42evqQIRibKlic4ppwib9N5jF33fFBE4uuzhLA5CdhJKzHVdV8ib9RBZwEHYpBI7pmDA1w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">是正则化系数。在实践中，采用</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503523722\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2689075630252101\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"238\" style=\"width:95px;height:26px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=52f92829&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42evqQIRibKlicu1wcD7HCY0X6UPFZVd0jFI3n243Y4sVmowQd7ozKmVPVx5abRph3Mw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，在早期时间鼓励更平滑的轨迹，而在</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503523723\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3958333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"96\" style=\"width:39px;height:20px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=66b6f5cf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42evqQIRibKlicFEicvuibSnIHGsjweuxaw6Dp2hSZxogcxulKmrCvpgbLLouhKyhjWSEg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">时则优先考虑准确性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">加速度正则项可以近似为：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503523724\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.12589073634204276\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"842\" style=\"width:331px;height:42px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f51a78cd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42evqQIRibKlic9vk2auIn2b9SLWR6w7ibcAibNx7GdnoyncPqnFZ4NcXBYVAicibhPnaoIA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">然而，该式难以直接计算，因为</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503523725\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8695652173913043\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"46\" style=\"width:26px;height:23px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9726d17e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42evqQIRibKlicqxtypgHGNV9biacKwNrFF64iaia2okmuxyiciaNrsCQfbr6KQjEuOHsRiaLw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">和&nbsp;</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503523726\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3877551020408163\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"98\" style=\"width:54px;height:21px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3b6f2eb6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42evqQIRibKlic1JftTMJePzcYrYH9OLSJLzhQUf1fZvCSL8NIUlGxM58vXnJngdpk8w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">位于同一条未知的流轨迹上。为克服这一困难，EfficientFlow 引入了流加速度上界（FABO）：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503523727\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.05555555555555555\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:475px;height:26px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6cabc2eb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42evqQIRibKlicictVM2VuBRklb409ZDE3HHaIH33WW3wVB7RiaCcTt6aBFXsrDQkjnL0w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">其中，</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503523728\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"46\" style=\"width:23px;height:23px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b616d189&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42evqQIRibKliczSbuLr3P1vbev093XeZlbV0hBaISJDSPnjlrh0zIIgZavFYATVcr8w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">和&nbsp;</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503523729\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4888888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"90\" style=\"width:45px;height:22px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d4355881&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42evqQIRibKlicLvZa3SEgkc3Rtia9QIFJ1FtesiaCW9ibOlFwoSJWxA2iaPbEHOEYVqUdqw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;来自同一个条件概率路径，很容易通过采样得到。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">本质上，FABO 是一个易于计算且有效的代理损失。同时，上界 FABO 与原式的差值等效于&nbsp;</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503523731\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.432\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"250\" style=\"width:72px;height:31px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0feb762c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42evqQIRibKlic5a0Licz4Tvfiag6RvcNTeImX0HTQQEHRHYic6iaibdrhNia4gVNBliczUUjWQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，可以看作对雅可比矩阵&nbsp;</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503523732\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3333333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"66\" style=\"width:20px;height:27px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1c7a9baa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42evqQIRibKlicNHvwouqtViaZx3RdNaplHNTSzdF2AEXWDMEroxDsOt9DX0qJ6YqoibJg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\">&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">的正则化，让模型生成的策略更稳、更鲁棒。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">2. 等变网络：让模型学会「举一反三」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">EfficientFlow 等变设计的核心逻辑非常直观：如果输入的视觉场景旋转了一定角度，那么机器人输出的动作自然也该跟随旋转相同的角度。这带来了巨大的数据优势，相当于一条数据就可以产生多条数据的效果。模型只需学习物体在一个角度下的操作，就能自动泛化到多个旋转角度，真正实现了「举一反三」。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503523733\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8130841121495327\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1070\" style=\"width:558px;height:454px;\" data-width=\"1078\" data-height=\"914\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/KmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42evqQIRibKlic9x8ZgFS960OibVDd3rnwJj5GaVnW2B28fzh6CSacfDnMopDDbMypBFA/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1070.3274021352313\" data-cropy1=\"30.690391459074732\" data-cropy2=\"901.5302491103203\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"490\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cc30fd53&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FKmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42evqQIRibKlicxB5px7Sqic4HribN2EZAs3f2m9g7e4Xd312OKGrSGuUmpfibicVcY1wk3w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">EfficientFlow 基于 escnn 库构建，将机器人在时间</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503523736\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8235294117647058\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"34\" style=\"width:23px;height:20px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=06cac4b3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42evqQIRibKlicjPia6vxPFibYOZbuqgtSQPvxZygOQbsPLWKicvpnd53DlkcnPic8S9Rulw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">的动作表示为一个 10 维向量&nbsp;</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503523737\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7619047619047619\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"42\" style=\"width:27px;height:21px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ccb58f64&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42evqQIRibKlicNC1xbPPjgPWcmuxFOIKAYuOibkY8TMunYFaPNJZzcnNTJ2lemNibVytg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，包含 6D 旋转表示、3D 平移向量和标量抓手宽度。动作输出对应的等变表示为：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503523738\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.10687022900763359\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"524\" style=\"width:251px;height:27px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4434a0ec&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42evqQIRibKlicOGniaDvp7XVqJMSksYSu5FtSVjDQoHBKs9odhja3mibRRic2ErxLSyGXw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这种表示使得</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503523739\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8695652173913043\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"46\" style=\"width:27px;height:23px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=151d8d8c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42evqQIRibKlicWQyKg4S69Z1dlicuWBB3xjY3zONVwF1uwbgZDXnjOxpRGFibLQVeaFVQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">能够生成遵循任务&nbsp;</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503523740\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.47058823529411764\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"102\" style=\"width:40px;height:20px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=114460fd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42evqQIRibKliclZTadrEG0YToBaELibWPqQ3mAATblibSAOOiaaRtcXQicRlPUDhWJgfRqg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\">&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">对称性的预测动作，从而确保在场景进行平面旋转时行为的一致性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">等变网络</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503523739\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8695652173913043\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"46\" style=\"width:27px;height:23px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=151d8d8c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42evqQIRibKlicWQyKg4S69Z1dlicuWBB3xjY3zONVwF1uwbgZDXnjOxpRGFibLQVeaFVQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">的输入是时间&nbsp;</span>t&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">、动作序列&nbsp;</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503523742\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9047619047619048\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"42\" style=\"width:24px;height:22px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7d839d33&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42evqQIRibKlic8Hqo8q5GEvMzVrJrSJ93Ge5oc0vyNn2ZUibGymzAZuqGksX3562tB1A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">和观测</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503523743\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"40\" style=\"width:22px;height:22px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=59692f6b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42